parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition module can cause the engine to stall, leading to a loss of power and potentially causing accidents, especially when driving at high speeds.
symptoms: The engine stalls
the vehicle loses power
the ignition module fails
the module needs to be replaced repeatedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The stalling of the vehicle can cause a loss of control, leading to accidents, especially when driving at high speeds or crossing intersections.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls
the engine loses power
the vehicle stalls while driving at high speeds
the vehicle stalls while crossing intersections.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Electrical System Failure (Air Conditioning Blower Motor Switch)
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the air conditioning blower motor switch can cause a fire, potentially leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The air conditioning blower motor switch melts
the wiring gets hot
the switch fails repeatedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the alternator harness plug connector can cause a short circuit, leading to a fire, potentially causing injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The alternator harness plug connector short circuits
the vehicle catches fire.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause a fire, potentially leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: A fire starts in the engine compartment
a fire starts near the steering wheel and dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Dual Fuel Tank Selector Valve Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the dual fuel tank selector valve can cause fuel leakage, which can lead to a fire when exposed to a source of ignition, posing a significant risk to vehicle occupants and other road users.
symptoms: Fuel leakage from the fuel tank
fuel spillage when filling the main tank
inability to switch to the main tank
vehicle stalls when the selector switch is on the front tank
limited range due to reliance on the auxiliary fuel tank.
